item.description:
City Sports Grille is inside Sparetime Manchester bowling alley, Maple Ave. & Valley St.

Karaoke is advertised as starting at 8 PM.

I would like to get there closer to 8 but cannot guarantee getting there before 9, because of an earlier commitment.

I have a co-host, Debra, who would like to find people to go bowling with there before karaoke.

There is a karaoke contest which might not start until as late as 10 PM.

There will be regular karaoke before the contest.

There is no contest entry fee.
